Simulated Region Labels for osmFISH Dataset

Source: R/data.R
osmFISH_metadata_region.Rd

A named character vector containing spatial region annotations for cells in the simulated osmFISH dataset. Each element corresponds to the region label assigned to a cell.

Usage

osmFISH_metadata_region

Format

A named character vector with length matching the number of cells. Names are cell IDs, and values represent spatial region names (e.g., "Region1", "Region2").

Source

Simulated spatial region assignment in osmFISH synthetic dataset.
